@node "future" "Future"

  @{b}Future@{ub}

  What's next?

  As  it seems that BED is not that widely used, that BAH is ever less used,
  and  the  feedback to its author (that is me) is even less, I have decided
  to  not continue to develop this program further. Possible enhancement and
  buf  fixes could or could not be made public (that is it may remain for my
  own  personal  use).  Included  in the features I wanted to add there were
  complete  metaframes  support  and  gfx icons for buttons (like in version
  2.0ć).
  
  I  may want to extend the usage of BAH engine to other programs with AREXX
  port,  such as ImageFX, ImageStudio, PageStream and Golded Studio, thought
  these will probably remain my own personal programs extensions.

@endnode

